code: @Override public LongType getRandom(Random rnd) {     return new LongType(rnd.nextLong()). }
@Override public void write(DataOutputView out) throws IOException {     out.writeLong(this.value). }
@Override public void read(DataInputView in) throws IOException {     this.value = in.readLong(). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj instanceof LongType) {         LongType other = (LongType) obj.         return this.value == other.value.     } else {         return false.     } }
